{
  "stem": "16106.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wore that striped uniform, and had this strange bosom, a bosom, was this little man with bosom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had sandwiches under those things, which I right away smelled like a dog.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stood there and stared at him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, would you like a-- would you like a sandwich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he gave me the sandwich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the whole friendship started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He taught me astrology, math, history.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, he was a walking encyclopedia, this lovely old man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a communist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he always said to me, I can't understand why the Jews are always [GERMAN], you know, bending with the SS.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't they just step on their toes that nobody sees, and all that big deal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, he was German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't-- and then he said, besides, I said, the Jews are all our enemies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was antisemitic on top of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Enemies, that means against the [INAUDIBLE] rich people, the bourgeoisie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm coming the working class, and so on and on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he took care of [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[GERMAN] was me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[GERMAN] means somebody whose nose is always running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Since [GERMAN] had a protector, I was saved from X, and, and, and, and Hannes, and the whole lot, where lots of girls had a lot of trouble with.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or maybe it wasn't trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I tell you what, it was always better than to die, whatever they did, although it was not very-- I can imagine, not pleasant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It is good looking girls, you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were in the camp, there's those little boys who had to take care of the-- of the SS and of the [GERMAN] of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
